  "title": "Junior Brand Assistant",
  "description": "<p>🚩 <strong>Looking for more than just a routine 9–5?</strong></p><p>Euphoria Organization is growing and seeking motivated individuals who are ready for clear career progression and long-term development.</p><p>📈 <strong>Merit-Based Career Advancement</strong><br />Promotions are based on performance and results — not tenure.</p><p>💸 <strong>Performance-Driven, Uncapped Earnings</strong><br />Your income reflects your effort, with no fixed ceiling.</p><p>🤝 <strong>Structured 1-to-1 Mentorship</strong><br />Personal coaching to ensure consistent learning and confidence in your role.</p><p>🧠 <strong>Professional & Leadership Development</strong><br />Ongoing training in communication, leadership, and marketing skills.</p><p>✈️ <strong>Performance-Based Travel Opportunities</strong><br />Regional exposure and networking for top performers.</p><p>No prior experience required — we value attitude, ambition, and willingness to learn.<br />📍 <strong>Singaporeans / PR only</strong></p>",
